=== One-time DHCP === <!--T:20-->

<!--T:21-->
To configure a network interface for one-time DHCP use issue the following command:

<!--T:22-->
{{RootCmd|dhcpcd eth0}}

<!--T:23-->
Be sure to replace <code>eth0</code> in the command above with the appropriate network interface name.

